{"tid":409842,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我同咗一個雙性戀同床瞓","createTime":"2017-09-22T11:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T10:51:51.000Z","uid":5271,"like":119,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"416628f643f25a8cc54e547333078b3d3f073d83","tid":409842,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟讀咗兩年Asso<br />\n終於升返上U，可以玩下Ocamp<br />\n同我同組有一位好Frd 嘅同學叫Dicky<br />\n有講有笑，開開心心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係玩City Hunt途中，佢不斷借啲兒撞我，仲周不時捉住我手臂<br />\n可能我暑假有做下Gym，佢想欣賞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入到Campsite，佢嘅行為愈嚟愈嚴重<br />\n成日攬住我，揸我屎忽同胸部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有次差啲揸中我碌鳩<br />\n我嗰陣心諗：鬼仔性格啫，外國好興咁熱親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到夜晚瞓覺，大家都知全房人會一齊鋪床褥係地下瞓<br />\n但因為唔夠位，我最後自己瞓咗床上面<br />\n而且張床係我一早霸定嘅<br />\n當時玩完房Game 太攰，好快瞓咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半夜醒咗先發現有個人瞓咗我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩個人瞓得勁埋，仲冚埋同一張被<br />\n望咗兩眼，佢仲一手扯走張被，搞到我冇被冚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為唔想再同佢拍埋瞓<br />\n最後我唯有頭對腳咁瞓埋半晚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到第二朝，佢一起身用就用啱啱瞓醒把聲講：<br />\n吓我搶咗你啲被呀？呀對唔住呀？你唔會嬲我架可？<br />\n我當堂打咗個冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：唔會，冇嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我都係咁避開佢<br />\n<br />\n到第二晚玩房Game 先知原來佢係雙性戀<br />\n我知道咗之後覺得好不安，好似洩底咗俾人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我一早知道就唔會俾佢咁搞我<br />\n請問各位巴打，咁樣有冇構成非禮罪？<br />\n<br />\n利申：我唔係其他歧視性別取向嘅人，但性別取向並唔可以透過觀察去得知<br />\n一般無法分辨佢係外國文化定想抽水，而佢都可能因為誤會我係同性戀，而不斷接觸我<br />\n<br />\n如果換轉係男性向女性做同樣事情，係香港一定可以告佢非禮或者遊蕩罪<br />\n<br />\n大家對性取向思覺變得開放，與此同時，應該將同性或異性之間的身體接觸一視同仁。<br />\n同性戀者或雙性戀者可以先表達自己取向，免得有構成誤會。"},{"pid":"7a558568bd44530de8d3b29320c802562a213d71","tid":409842,"uid":67933,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d0037d496322e2438d07716993ff1fe16d541a","tid":409842,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07b80e317444ca075d1947d76c2129dda9b731a","tid":409842,"uid":55511,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"其實你都係雙性戀 係你唔知姐"},{"pid":"3e8099eaa2c4f22ec1c3b6de90a5434be8d1a020","tid":409842,"uid":107571,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:01:45.000Z","msg":"1010<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228038f494e611a92ba61006e2677f933408fec0","tid":409842,"uid":138474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc3d73bcff0d5c6ba1231879b979aa5ac73dcb0","tid":409842,"uid":34623,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:07:27.000Z","msg":"讀asso玩asshole<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce4e0a58265cf14346b8a19aaaf153f847d31e7","tid":409842,"uid":120202,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"gym巴打好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主一定係黑實大隻靚仔 求tf<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2c2525f2f06efa63a8bac16e19eac7d9271e00","tid":409842,"uid":136038,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:20:47.000Z","m